perm_subclass(perm_id) -> (new_perm_id, control_channel, spawner)
subclass permissions to make a new set of permissions that are the same or less than the original

perm_delete(perm_id)
deletes the permission and terminates processess spawned with that perm's and any subperm's spawner

connect(perm_id, service) -> (service_channel)
connects to a given service
